Description: The rest on the flight into Egypt, the Virgin is seated holding the Christ Child in a landscape in the centre, Joseph occurs in the upper left with the donkey that looks to the right Etching
Curator's comments: This is not described by Bartsch. The print is unfinished. The figure of Joseph and the donkey in the upper left are in outline only.
Exhibition history: 2007 Sep-Dec, Rancate, Pinacoteca Giovanni Züst, 'Camillo Procaccini...'
